http://www.freefavicon.com/index.php

    Click "Download Favicon", download package, unzip it and then open it. Your favicon.ico is located in it.
    Upload the favicon.ico file to your web site root folder (make sure it goes into your root directory where your index page is located).
    Between your <head> and </head> tags enter the follow code: <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
    Just read the text file that comes in the .zip and you can begin using your new favicon asap!
